   OMB No. 0925-0299
   Expiration Date: 03/31/2003
   NIH Academy Program
   For recent college graduates who have an interest in health disparities
   If you have already applied to the Postbaccalaureate IRTA program and
   would also like to apply to the NIH Academy program click here to
   modify your application.


   Instructions: Before you begin, you may want to review some helpful
   hints on using electronic forms and a statement about privacy. After
   you fill out the application form below, press the [Preview] button at
   the bottom of this page to review your application for accuracy.
   Eligibility Criteria:
   1. Candidates must have graduated from a fully accredited U.S. College
   or University no more than 1 year prior to the activation date of
   traineeship.
   2. Candidates must be U.S. citizens or permanent residents and intend
   to apply to graduate or medical school within the next year.

